anecdotal:

100-200 words/page on average for books (2-400 in typed print)

40k+ words for a novel
17.5-40k words for a novella
7.5-17.5k words for a novelette
50-7.5k words for a short story

1 ml ink:
15-45 pages of shorthand
10-15 pages of longhand
5-10 pages of illuminated manuscript/direct copy

speed:
shorthand - up to 350 wpm
longhand - up to 20 wpm
illuminated - up to 5 wpm